<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tri Thức — Luyện thi trắc nghiệm</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;1,500&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Spectral+SC:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --ink: #1c2a24;
    --paper: #faf7f0;
    --moss: #3e5f4d;
    --moss-deep: #2a463b;
    --gold: #b89d4f;
    --gold-soft: #dac880;
    --line: rgba(28,42,36,0.12);
    --shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(28,42,36,0.12);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0;}
  body{
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    color:var(--ink);
    background:var(--paper);
    min-height:100vh;
    overflow-x:hidden;
    line-height:1.5;
    letter-spacing:0.3px;
  }
  ::selection{background:var(--gold-soft); color:var(--moss-deep);}

  #landing{
    position:relative;
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:60px 32px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 20%, rgba(185,137,63,0.1), transparent 45%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 82% 78%, rgba(60,91,72,0.15), transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #fdfbf8 0%, #faf7f0 60%, #f5f1e6 100%);
  }
  #landing::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; inset:0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    opacity:0.25;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 70% at 50% 50%, black 30%, transparent 80%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .landing-mark{
    position:absolute;
    top:36px;
    left:50%;
    transform:translateX(-50%);
    font-family:'Spectral SC', serif;
    font-size:15px;
    letter-spacing:0.32em;
    color:var(--moss);
    opacity:0.75;
  }
  .landing-inner{
    position:relative;
    max-width:880px;
    z-index:2;
    animation: riseIn 1.1s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.25,1) both;
  }
  @keyframes riseIn{
    from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(22px);}
    to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
  }
  .quote-mark{
    font-family:'Lora', serif;
    font-style:italic;
    font-size:64px;
    color:var(--gold);
    line-height:0.5;
    margin-bottom:18px;
    display:block;
  }
  .landing-quote{
    font-family:'Lora', serif;
    font-weight:600;
    font-style:italic;
    font-size:clamp(32px, 5.2vw, 58px);
    line-height:1.28;
    color:var(--moss-deep);
    margin:0 0 14px 0;
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }
  .landing-sub{
    font-size:17px;
    color:#5b6a5f;
    letter-spacing:0.04em;
    margin:0 0 44px 0;
  }
  .cta-link{
    position:relative;
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:18px;
    letter-spacing:0.02em;
    color:#f6f2e2;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--moss) 0%, var(--moss-deep) 100%);
    border:none;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:18px 42px;
    text-decoration:none;
    cursor:pointer;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: transform .35s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1), box-shadow .35s ease;
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
  }
  .cta-link:hover{
    transform:translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(28,42,36,0.26);
  }
  .cta-link:active{transform:translateY(0px) scale(0.98);}
  .cta-link svg{transition:transform .35s ease;}
  .cta-link:hover svg{transform:translateX(4px);}
  .landing-foot{
    margin-top:54px;
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:0.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:#8b8870;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section id="landing">
  <span class="landing-mark">TRI THỨC · LUYỆN THI</span>
  <div class="landing-inner">
    <span class="quote-mark">“</span>
    <h1 class="landing-quote">Nếu bạn muốn chinh phục thế giới,<br>hãy bắt đầu bằng việc mở rộng tri thức của chính mình.</h1>
    <p class="landing-sub">Một không gian luyện tập trắc nghiệm tĩnh lặng, được thiết kế cho sự tập trung.</p>
    <a href="practice.html" class="cta-link">
      Bắt đầu kết nối với Tri thức
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8H13M13 8L9 4M13 8L9 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </a>
    <div class="landing-foot">Phiếu trả lời trắc nghiệm · Đếm giờ · Tra cứu mã đề</div>
  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
